Indition?

69
00:04:43.350 --> 00:04:45.090
Well, we might have to remember.

70
00:04:45.090 --> 00:04:48.630
We might have to think about,
well have I heard this before?

71
00:04:48.630 --> 00:04:50.980
And that might involve the hippocampus.

72
00:04:50.980 --> 00:04:55.080
And there is a vast and
certainly not fully understood

73
