how we feel about the music.

77
00:05:14.250 --> 00:05:16.800
Which to some measure,
is the responsibility

78
00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:21.720
of another part of the brain,
the limbic system, including the amygdala.

79
00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:23.420
Whew, it is complicated.

80
00:05:24.420 --> 00:05:27.820
Maybe the brain is as
mysterious as music itself.

81
00:05:29.290 --> 00:05:31.320
And while we're on
the subject of music and

82
00:05:31.320 --> 00:05:36.870
the brain, let's think about how it is
that music excites us or relaxes us.

83
00:05:36.870 --> 00:05:41.320
Gets us pumped up to lift weights,
or run, or calms us down at night.

84
00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:47.110
In our brain,
information about sound is transformed,

85
