such as dopamine and glutamates.

87
00:05:55.570 --> 00:06:00.050
These move from one cell to the next,
exciting or inhibiting

88
00:06:00.050 --> 00:06:04.330
the neighboring cells causing us in one
way or another to get excited or to relax.

